{"tid":1963070,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"班醫護應該好撚憎林鄭月娥","createTime":"2020-04-08T01:34:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-08T01:53:48.000Z","uid":74778,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a8b2013d0a60e85027cb14dd63f1d687da6b2961","tid":1963070,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T01:34:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好撚高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n拍手就可以抗疫？<br />\n<br />\n話支持醫護？你開會開到失憶？<br />\n當我哋喺前線面對武肺，你哋班膠官留喺 office 拍手。<br />\n當我哋以罷工明志要求封關，你哋班膠官唔聽。<br />\n然後有個乜9藍色團體話拍手，你哋班膠官即刻仆去做。<br />\nAre you kidding me? <br />\n<br />\n今日，我哋喺前線唔夠物資，你哋班膠官做緊乜？<br />\n777 加人工，袁國勇諫言講事實被人噤聲，大聲公講嘢係襲擊<br />\n黃店同藍店popo 檢查標準不一，九個月嚟無一個popo被追究，<br />\n係一個都無！<br />\n<br />\n講到尾，一個唔民主嘅制度，<br />\n只聽權貴嘅指點，不理人民死活。<br />\n<br />\n未來，我哋對政權已無希望。<br />\n制度已死，退無可退，別無他法，唯有決志攬炒！<br />\n<br />\n#拍手抗疫<br />\n#好諗嘢<br />\n#你物資唔夠我加人工<br />\n#我地要35+<br />\n#進入立法會嗰日起即刻反對所有議案<br />\n#我哋要全面真攬炒<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9FBnt05.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9FBnt05.jpg&h=8f126d22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HA.EmployAlliance/photos/a.116961523108322/158009549003519/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHA.EmployAlliance%2Fphotos%2Fa.116961523108322%2F158009549003519%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=LgTIxyFtuo0acoW68XVTBWVlCuV5KOpEhASsqV1EMe4%3D&h=84c5118b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HA.EmployAlliance/photos/a.116961523108322/158009549003519/?type=3</a>"},{"pid":"75a8096538a2fc63dc3fbd88c1919e8e230999d6","tid":1963070,"uid":220431,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T01:46:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5DjkfK9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5DjkfK9.png&h=d14e598c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"86e6af7bd0211d9efd78a1630